<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFB06A0FF825974C17CBBAE6" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFB06A0FF825974C17CBBAE6" blockId="75.[2006,2602,277,704]" pageId="75" pageNumber="833">
Form 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF7D3974C16A8BA04" authorityName="J. A. Allen" authorityYear="1917" box="[2095,2216,277,310]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="humeralis">humeralis</taxonomicName>
has been previously treated under 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF7BD976416C1BA6C" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[2113,2241,317,350]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">G. beatrix</taxonomicName>
, but they are tentatively treated as separate species here. A. Hassanin and colleagues in 2018 retrieved 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF62A97D21605BAE6" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">G. beatrix</taxonomicName>
as sister to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF75E97EA1723BAE6" authorityName="Eger &amp; Schlitter" authorityYear="2001" box="[2210,2339,435,468]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="curryae">G. curryae</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
